      "$description": "The sole typeface — a custom geometric sans used at every scale. Weight 400 carries the editorial body and nav; weight 500 appears on buttons and emphasized labels. The 96px display at 0.96 line-height with -0.04em tracking is the system's signature: it compresses into a dense confident block rather than stretching vertically, making the headline feel sculptural."
